column5: Wow...you got the whole family...I counted 38.
Perch are illegal to use as bait
You can tell by the way they are all alligned in the same North/South orientation that they are so full of mercury that it re-acts to the Earth's magnetic field!
You better not let Jethro see you with those!!!  Mmmmmmmmmmm!... Magnetic Perch!!!
Good to get in a few provisions before the storm Jed !

Paul can I go fishin with you >I could save alot of time fishin with you.  Lets see 7 hour drive for me to simcoe half hour of fishing 38 perch .ya it would be worth the drive.  Where did you get such a powerful shopvac.Where's the pics of Tarpus maximus?  You always post them  MTP
Be careful what you beleive.  Remember the track record fer truth tellin' among fishermen.
